      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical R2022 is a commercially validated solver with documented QA procedures including regression test suites and ISO 9001 certification. FDA in-house scripts are version-controlled in a validated repository. Required level 2 is met."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
